reviewText: Old film reels mostly about politics. No toys of the time. No music of the time. Nobody liked it. Bad Bad

THIS is one of the good ones -- IF you can live with the fact that the producers crammed TWO wonderful planes into ONE film and used 1940s technology (what choice?).  I've been living on a borrowed copy and finally found this source to get my own.
I like the Kittyhawk and Lightning alot and... I'm sorry but I can't think of anything to say!
